{"tid":1328390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[向新鴻基宣戰第一擊]新鴻基樓巴絲不合作運動","createTime":"2019-07-18T01:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T03:15:02.000Z","uid":34342,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ffea4210770adec07dc77351a8da620726db8254","tid":1328390,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:55:00.000Z","msg":"宜加大部分新鴻基樓都係啟勝（新鴻基子公司)負責管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁咪好容易又放警察入來？</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有住戶冇交管理費，應該係會由業主立案法團埋單（管理公司點都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係</span> 管理公司都要幫手追數！<br />\n<br />\n詳情請參考：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/688393/日報-港聞-欠管理費13年-神隱戶主變白骨\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F688393%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%AC%A0%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%B2%BB13%E5%B9%B4-%E7%A5%9E%E9%9A%B1%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%BB%E8%AE%8A%E7%99%BD%E9%AA%A8&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=cb715df4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F688393%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%AC%A0%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%B2%BB13%E5%B9%B4-%E7%A5%9E%E9%9A%B1%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%BB%E8%AE%8A%E7%99%BD%E9%AA%A8&h=f40342ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/688393/日報-港聞-欠管理費13年-神隱戶主變白骨</a><br />\n<br />\n我朋友發夢好多年前管理公司串77，所以唔交管理費，直至三個月後佢寄律師信來先交，最後要管理公司上門道歉了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街一定要準時交管理費，唔好煩到啟勝啲哥哥姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">SHK = SELL HONG KONG </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一步查下屋契等嘅文件，睇下點樣合法地再搞鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6665e1d0edd32f100e44261c05d6f007a474727b","tid":1328390,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"【\b721文宣】星期日前一齊做鍵盤戰士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327641</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXAdLRx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXAdLRx.jpg&h=988ba3dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aw6P3Dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faw6P3Dd.jpg&h=545a2bea&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxBsQid.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxBsQid.jpg&h=0a25f5ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DEt65Rz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDEt65Rz.png&h=d8e97094&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vHzvie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vHzvie.jpg&h=38ca5e73&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFsr5Rz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFsr5Rz.png&h=df834da0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb4462f1111499438cb20c0202